Sentencas: The layered GdBa0.5Sr0.5Co2O5+delta (GBSC) perovskite oxides are synthesized by Pechini method and investigated as a novel cathode material for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: Layered GdBa0.5Sr0.5Co2O5+δ as a cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The single cell of NiO-SDC (Sm0.2Ce0.8O1.9)/SDC (similar to 20 mu m)/GBSC (similar to 10 mu m) is operated from 550 to 700 degrees C fed with humidified H-2 as fuel and the static air as oxidant.
Titulo: Layered GdBa0.5Sr0.5Co2O5+δ as a cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: An open circuit voltage of 0.8 V and a maximum power density of 725 mW cm(-2) are achieved at 700 degrees C.
Titulo: Layered GdBa0.5Sr0.5Co2O5+δ as a cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The interfacial polarization resistance is as low as 0.88, 0.29, 0.13 and 0.05 Omega cm(2) at 550, 600, 650 and 700 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Layered GdBa0.5Sr0.5Co2O5+δ as a cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The ratio of polarization resistance to total cell resistance decreases with the increase in the operating temperature, from 60% at 550 degrees C to 21% at 700 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Layered GdBa0.5Sr0.5Co2O5+δ as a cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The experimental results indicate that GBSC is a promising cathode material for IT-SOFCs.
Titulo: Layered GdBa0.5Sr0.5Co2O5+δ as a cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells
